item.title: CVE-2023-26102|2023-02-24T05:00:01.144Z -- n%2Fa -- rangy
item.description: All versions of the package rangy are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution when using the extend() function in file rangy-core.js.The function uses recursive merge which can lead an attacker to modify properties of the Object.prototype
